import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import styles from './Menu.module.css'

  const Menu = () => {
    return (
      <nav className={styles.menu}>
        <NavLink
          end
          to="."
          className={styles.menuLink}
          activeClassName={styles.active}
        >
          Home
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink to="rent" className={styles.menuLink} activeClassName={styles.active}>
          Rent
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink to="buysell" className={styles.menuLink} activeClassName={styles.active}>
          BuySell
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink to="housing" className={styles.menuLink} activeClassName={styles.active}>
          Housing
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink to="commercial" className={styles.menuLink} activeClassName={styles.activeLink}>
          Commercial
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink to="architecture" className={styles.menuLink} activeClassName={styles.activeLink}>
          Architecture
        </NavLink>
      </nav>
    );
}

export default Menu
